  "kind": "Definition",
  "title": "Tail Infimum Sequence",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $(x_n)$ be a bounded real sequence. The \\textbf{tail infimum\nsequence} of $(x_n)$ is the real sequence $(i_n)$ defined by\n\\[\n i_n:=\\inf\\{x_k:k\\ge n\\}\n \\qquad\\text{for every } n\\in\\mathbb{N}.\n\\]",
